Call Bradley.description: Call Bradley (check none is out or being looted before using!)
commands: say Bradley called by $player.name. Please do not interfere with it.

Call CH47.description: Calls the Chinook to you (please only use if no Chinook is out)
commands: say Chinook called by $player.name, to their location. Please do not interfere with it.

Call Heli.description: Calls the Heli extremely close to you (please only use if no heli is out)
commands: say Heli called by $player.name, to their location. Please do not interfere with it.
say Thanks $player.name for the mass air drop!
say Thanks $player.name for the supply signal!

Remove Heli.description: Removes Heli from the map (not to be used if the heli is being fought)

Reycler.description: Recycler for your base, check your bag

commands: say use /STOP to stop a horse from moving

Surprise!.displayName: Spawns a random suprise on you...
Surprise!.description: Spawns a random animal on you, yes seriously

Christmas_All.description: Triggers All the Christmas events for everyone
